she moved from Hawaii

18:15.896 --> 18:16.837
to St. Louis?

18:16.838 --> 18:18.564
Yes, I am.

18:18.598 --> 18:20.956
And as soon as I give Sandra the shot,

18:21.222 --> 18:23.197
our deal is over.

18:23.198 --> 18:24.289
Fine, good.

18:24.527 --> 18:25.580
Marcus!

18:27.140 --> 18:28.495
That was just foreplay, all right?

18:28.502 --> 18:29.945
We're about to get this thing going!

18:29.946 --> 18:31.911
Sandra, lift your shirt.

18:31.945 --> 18:33.546
Marcus, take off your shirt!

18:33.580 --> 18:35.714
Fair warning, I still have
a bit of a Thanksgiving paunch

18:35.749 --> 18:37.883
I'm working off.
All right, this is happening.

18:37.918 --> 18:40.452
Oh, oh, oh, well, you know
what else is happening?

18:40.487 --> 18:42.021
This thing over here!
Yeah, look at this!

18:42.055 --> 18:43.289
Here we go!

18:43.323 --> 18:45.691
- Take this off!
- Come on, go, go, go!

18:45.725 --> 18:47.560
Guys, guys, guys!

18:47.594 --> 18:50.462
You both know what you're
doing, so stop pretending!

18:50.497 --> 18:53.265
Glenn, you obviously
don't want to use Sandra.

18:53.300 --> 18:55.234
Of course I don't want to use Sandra.

18:55.268 --> 18:57.017
