18:57.018 --> 18:58.625
You think I want to
have sex with Marcus?

18:58.626 --> 19:00.272
He starts every time by saying,

19:00.307 --> 19:01.772
"I'm not really sure what
I'm doing down there."

19:01.773 --> 19:03.520
Oh, sorry for being honest.

19:03.521 --> 19:06.398
Well, both of you clearly
want this, so just get over it.

19:06.746 --> 19:07.716
Fine with me.

19:08.481 --> 19:09.379
All right.

19:15.989 --> 19:16.788
So...

19:19.292 --> 19:21.240
I guess we should go back to work.

19:21.241 --> 19:23.495
Are you hitting on me?

19:23.530 --> 19:25.313
I honestly... I can't tell anymore.

19:26.398 --> 19:27.758
Hey.

19:28.021 --> 19:29.966
Hey, join us.

19:30.530 --> 19:32.438
So you two are getting along.

19:32.472 --> 19:34.773
Yeah, we worked it all out.

19:34.808 --> 19:36.065
Good, good.

19:36.066 --> 19:38.471
See? All it needed was a little
bit of communication...

19:38.472 --> 19:42.147
Amy, we're gonna need you
to engage meaningfully

19:42.182 --> 19:43.148
for a minute.

19:43.183 --> 19:43.982
I'm sorry, what?

19:43.983 --> 19:45.853
Shh! You're not engaging.

19:46.319 --> 19:48.320
Look, I love you, but sometimes,

19:48.355 --> 19:50.623
