19:53.326 --> 19:55.160
or that my yearbook quote shouldn't be,

19:55.195 --> 19:56.955
"Catch me outside, how 'bout that?"

19:56.956 --> 19:59.331
Yeah, I was just saying that
yearbooks are permanent.

19:59.366 --> 20:01.033
You're pushy, you're manipulative,

20:01.067 --> 20:02.768
and you were super mean about Bo.

20:02.802 --> 20:06.005
Ooh, are you burning Amy?
I got a good one.

20:06.039 --> 20:08.155
Your hair. Boom.

20:09.592 --> 20:10.637
That was harsh.

20:11.065 --> 20:13.370
I don't know, man,
I mean, today it's angels,

20:13.371 --> 20:15.781
tomorrow it's, let's go ghost hunting.

20:15.815 --> 20:17.950
Look, man, Kelly is cool, she's fun,

20:17.992 --> 20:19.115
you guys should go away together.

20:19.116 --> 20:22.210
Yeah, well, maybe we will.
Just not this weekend.

20:23.056 --> 20:23.892
No.

20:25.225 --> 20:26.396
You have something special,

20:26.397 --> 20:27.566
and you're gonna throw it all away

20:27.567 --> 20:29.561
'cause she sees an angel or two?

20:29.596 --> 20:30.693
